<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 03:14:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>地缘政治担忧削弱信心，亚洲股市下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周二下跌，因投资者思考美国即将降息，并等待人工智能宠儿英伟达的财报，而中东紧张局势加剧和供应担忧抑制了风险情绪并提振了油价。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 02:19:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国军队侵犯领空的行为完全不可接受</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-militarys-airspace-violation-is-utterly-unacceptable-japan-says-2024-08-27/</link><description>日本政府高级发言人周二表示，中国军机侵犯日本领空的行为“完全不可接受”。一天前，日本紧急升空并召见中国驻东京大使馆官员以示抗议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 02:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-militarys-airspace-violation-is-utterly-unacceptable-japan-says-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国是该地区和平的“最大破坏者”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-is-biggest-disruptor-peace-region-2024-08-27/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周二表示，中国是该地区国际和平的最大破坏者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:44:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-is-biggest-disruptor-peace-region-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>中东风险削弱降息乐观情绪，货币停滞不前</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-water-middle-east-risks-temper-rate-cut-optimism-2024-08-27/</link><description>周二美元小幅走高，主要货币横盘整理，因对中东紧张局势的持续担忧部分抵消了投资者对美国即将降息的乐观情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:32:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-water-middle-east-risks-temper-rate-cut-optimism-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国2023年太平洋演习花费153亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-spent-153-bln-pacific-exercises-2023-internal-taiwan-estimates-show-2024-08-27/</link><description>根据台湾此前未公布的估计，中国在 2023 年在西太平洋演习的支出约为 150 亿美元，即其国防预算的 7%，这显示了北京对台湾及其邻国周围军事活动的投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 01:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-spent-153-bln-pacific-exercises-2023-internal-taiwan-estimates-show-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：沿着美国利率路径小心翼翼地前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 21:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>郑通过阿尼西莫娃测试进入美国公开赛第二轮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-passes-anisimova-test-reach-us-open-second-round-2024-08-26/</link><description>周一，奥运冠军郑钦文克服了发球初期的困境，以4-6 6-4 6-2的苦战战胜了美国外卡选手阿曼达·阿尼西莫娃，进入美国公开赛第二轮。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:59:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-passes-anisimova-test-reach-us-open-second-round-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国公开赛第一天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/us-open-day-one-2024-08-26/</link><description>周一在法拉盛草地举行的美国公开赛第一天的亮点（格林威治标准时间）：</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 15:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/us-open-day-one-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大将对包括特斯拉在内的中国电动汽车征收100%关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trudeau-says-canada-impose-100-tariff-chinese-evs-2024-08-26/</link><description>继美国和欧盟之后，加拿大周一表示将对中国电动汽车进口征收100%的关税，并宣布对从中国进口的钢铁和铝征收25%的关税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/trudeau-says-canada-impose-100-tariff-chinese-evs-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国拼多多因市场不确定而市值缩水400亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/temu-owner-pdd-holdings-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国拼多多周一季度营收未达到市场预期，高管对中国国内电子商务竞争和公司全球前景的悲观评论导致其股价下跌超过 28%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/temu-owner-pdd-holdings-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>日本出动战机紧急起飞攻击侵犯领空的中国飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/japan-scrambles-jets-against-china-reconnaissance-plane-that-breached-airspace-2024-08-26/</link><description>日本防卫省表示，周一上午，一架中国侦察机短暂侵犯日本领空，日本防卫省已紧急紧急升空。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:21:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/japan-scrambles-jets-against-china-reconnaissance-plane-that-breached-airspace-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国机器人大会聚焦类人机器人的变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国正试图用更便宜、更具创新性的零部件在人形机器人开发领域取得领先地位。一些高管表示，该行业尚未提高产品可靠性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 06:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-robots-conference-spotlights-changing-face-humanoids-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国工业界寻求缓解拜登-哈里斯对中国关税的大幅上调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</link><description>削减关税可能会招致共和党人的批评，称哈里斯将对中国采取更温和的立场。继续加息会招致成本上升的抱怨，甚至来自民主党。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 05:07:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-industry-seeks-easing-steep-biden-harris-china-tariff-hikes-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国在南海的举动具有侵略性且非法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</link><description>过去一周发生一系列空中和海上冲突和事件后，菲律宾政府周一谴责中国在南海“一再采取侵略性、不专业和非法的”行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:20:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-actions-south-china-sea-patently-illegal-philippine-defence-min-says-2024-08-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队将在中缅边境举行武装巡逻和实弹演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</link><description>中国军方周一表示，随着缅甸执政军政府和叛军之间的战斗升级，中国军方已在中缅边境附近组织军队和空地警察联合巡逻，以维护安全稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 00:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-military-says-it-conducted-armed-patrols-joint-police-patrols-near-china-2024-08-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>